Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.10,0:45:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但没想到会以这种形式出现
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.29,0:45:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 异世界的圣机师物语
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.84,0:45:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『袭来』
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.96,0:45:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我们绝对会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.52,0:45:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧